<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What Happens to My Dogecoin Held in Paypal if I Decide to Close My Paypal Account, and Are There Any Specific Procedures for Withdrawing or Transferring Dogecoin Before Account Closure?</h3>



<p>If you close your PayPal account, you must transfer your Dogecoin due to wallet compatibility issues. Without account reactivation, you&#8217;ll lose access. Ensure you understand the withdrawal process to safeguard your assets effectively.</p>



